		(uuid "153faacb-0678-40ea-b37d-0e06ada9b2a1")
	)
	(text "Extra Outputs (AMP Superseal 1.0 26 Pin)\n\nLS_OUT are 3.5A lowside drivers intended e.g.\nrelay, 	\n3.5A continuous, has external flyback diode\n\nLS_HOT_OUT are lowside drivers e.g.\ninjector\n3.5A continuous, has no flyback diode\n\n\nDC is H-bridge e.g.\nETB, EWG, any DC motor\n6A continuous\n\n5V_OUT are 5V LOGIC Outputs e.g.\nSmart coils\n24mA source/sink\n\n\nLS_HOT1-2 ALSO CONNECTED TO BATCH FIRE \nPINS ON STOCK HARNESS\n\n5V_OUT1 ALSO CONNECTED TO DISTRIBUTOR \nIGNITER TRIGGER ON STOCK HARNESS\n\nThis is done to allow easy conversion from batch \nand distibutor to sequential"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 327.406 64.516 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "220fa155-7419-47dd-8e0e-684115dab7cb")
	)
	(text "Extra Event / Switch Inputs (2.54mm Pin Header)\nDC1-4 Is fastest, ideal for PWM input (flex fuel, etc)\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
